title: Highly Sought-After Address in Premier School District
posting_body: ['The Prescott at Concord', '1 Nathan Pratt Drive, Concord, MA, 01742', 'Call Now - (978) 592-7573 x 15', 'OR Text', '15', 'to', '(978) 592-7573', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'Sun filled apartments in quiet community', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 719 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'When it comes to apartment rentals in The Prescott at Concord, there’s really just one choice.', 'With our one-, two- and three-bedroom apartment and town home floor plans, you will surely find a space that suits your needs.', 'Whether you want to play, relax, or gather with friends,The Prescott at Concord Apartments provide countless options with uncommon community amenities at every turn.', 'Relax beside a sparkling pool, enjoy the warmth of an outdoor fire pit or play a game of bocce ball as you unwind after a day of work.', 'Enjoy the perks of life at a residential community that offers a bark park, children’s playgrounds, and private garages and storage spaces.', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.', 'Pet Policy', 'We welcome 2 pets per apartment home.', 'Pet rent is $65 for dogs and $50 for cats.', 'Maximum allowed weight is 100lbs.', 'Please call for complete pet policy information.', 'Income Requirements:', 'This apartment is part of the Massachusetts 40B Affordable Program.', 'Participant must meet income requirements.', 'Minimum Annual Income', '1BR- $42,000', '2BR- $46,536', '3BR- $51,096', 'Maximum Annual Gross Income Limit', 'Household Size:', '1 Person Household: $70,750', '2 Person Household: $80,850', '3 Person Household: $90,950', '4 Person Household: $101,050', '5 Person Household: $109,150', '6 Person Household: $117,250', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', '4nSs6lVj7Bn']
